# mehfil.DEV Design System

> Reference: https://mehfilai.framer.website — use as design north-star for layout hierarchy, section structure, pricing tables, FAQ, and CTA patterns.

## Visual Identity

**Dark crimson engineering aesthetic.** Pure-black base, crimson + rose-red accents, deep-red ambient glows, glassmorphism panels, monospace labels. Mirrors `https://mehfilai.framer.website`.

## Color Tokens

> Legacy `matrix-green*` / `aquamarine` keys are retained as aliases that now resolve to crimson values.
> Use the `crimson*` / `rose` tokens below in new code.

| Token | Hex | Use |
|-------|-----|-----|
| `base` | `#000000` | Page background |
| `surface` | `#0C0C0F` | Card/panel fill |
| `subtle` | `#232328` | Borders, dividers |
| `crimson` | `#E11D48` | Primary CTA, accents |
| `crimson-light` | `#FB7185` | Hover states, neon labels |
| `crimson-muted` | `#4C0519` | Muted crimson fills |
| `rose` | `#F43F5E` | Secondary accent |
| `text-main` | `#FFFFFF` | Body text |
| `text-muted` | `#9CA3AF` | Secondary text |
| `text-neon` | `#FB7185` | Labels, badges, neon text |

## Typography

- **Headings:** Inter, `font-bold` or `font-extrabold`, gradient text via `.text-gradient-hero` or `.text-gradient-accent`
- **Body:** Inter, `text-text-muted` for secondary content
- **Labels/badges:** JetBrains Mono, `font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-text-neon`
- **Code snippets:** `font-mono text-matrix-green`

## CSS Component Classes

| Class | Use |
|-------|-----|
| `.glass-panel` | Standard card surface |
| `.glass-panel-strong` | Hero/featured card |
| `.glow-border` | Hover gradient border effect |
| `.text-gradient-hero` | White→mint→cyan gradient heading |
| `.text-gradient-accent` | Green→cyan gradient text |
| `.btn-primary` | Primary CTA (green, glowing) |
| `.btn-glass` | Secondary CTA (glass dark) |
| `.section-label` | Pill badge above section headings |
| `.browser-frame` | Dark browser chrome mockup |
| `.dot-grid-bg` | Dot grid section background |
| `.line-grid-bg` | Line grid section background |

## Section Layout Pattern

Every section follows this exact hierarchy (inspired by mehfil AI reference):

```tsx
<section id="section-id" className="relative py-24 sm:py-32">
  {/* 1. Section label pill */}
  <span className="section-label">// LABEL TEXT</span>

  {/* 2. Heading with gradient accent */}
  <h2 className="text-4xl font-bold">
    Plain text{" "}
    <span className="text-gradient-accent">Accented word</span>
  </h2>

  {/* 3. Subheading in text-muted */}
  <p className="text-text-muted text-lg max-w-2xl">...</p>

  {/* 4. Content cards in grid */}
  <div className="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-16">
    <div className="glass-panel glow-border rounded-xl p-6">...</div>
  </div>
</section>
```

## Pricing Card Pattern (mehfil AI Reference)

Three tiers: Basic / Standard / Premium (maps to Professional / Small Team / Enterprise from reference).

```tsx
// Featured card gets ring-1 ring-matrix-green + glass-panel-strong
// Non-featured gets glass-panel
// All tiers: price → spec list → feature list → CTA button
```

## Spacing

- Section padding: `py-24 sm:py-32`
- Container: `max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8`
- Card gap: `gap-6` (standard) or `gap-8` (featured)
- Internal card padding: `p-6` (standard) or `p-8` (featured)

## Animation Conventions

- Entrance: `opacity: 0 → 1`, `y: 30 → 0`, duration `0.6s`
- Stagger children with 0.1s delay increments (`.stagger-1` through `.stagger-5`)
- Hover transforms: `hover:-translate-y-1` on cards
- Glow pulses: `animate-pulse-glow` on primary CTAs

## Do NOT

- Add light mode styles — dark only
- Use raw hex colors in JSX — use Tailwind tokens
- Add new font families — Inter and JetBrains Mono only
- Use `@apply` in new CSS — inline Tailwind classes preferred
- Add shadows not using `rgba(0,0,0,*)` or `rgba(16,185,129,*)` — keep to palette
